Articles.Content: Ok, so heres my problem, i am trying to take the standard fuel tank and make it able to hold more. So i took the fuel tank folder, duplicated it and went in the duplicate. I open part.cfg and change the fuel = 400.0 to fuel = 1000.0. When i start the game, i hold my mouse over the part and it says 1000. When i add it to a rocket and start the game, and right click it, it says there\'s only 400 fuel left. What do i do?

You need to change the Name= parameter in the config or the game can\'t tell your new part from the old part.

Cheers!

Capt\'n Skunky

KSP Community Manager
